00:14:49.376 --> 00:14:50.528
And we get four

00:14:50.336 --> 00:14:51.904
with excitement.

00:14:52.032 --> 00:14:54.432
And may we share the good news.

00:14:54.240 --> 00:14:56.832
Of Jesus Christ to all those

00:14:56.672 --> 00:14:58.080
That are around us.

00:14:58.368 --> 00:14:59.584
Let us pray.
